EN: When I see her smile, my mood becomes very happy.

ZH: 当我听到这个消息时，我感到非常震惊。
EN: When I heard this news, I was very shocked.

ZH: 当他来找我时，我已经离开了。
EN: When he came to find me, I had already left.

ZH: 当他发现自己迷路时，他感到非常沮丧。
EN: When he realized he was lost, he felt very frustrated.

ZH: 当我去超市时，我会买一些水果。
EN: When I go to the supermarket, I will buy some fruits.

ZH: 当天黑了之后，他才离开公园。
EN: He didn't leave the park until it got dark.

