EN: He always offers help when he wants to.

ZH: 当你需要我的时候，我会全力支持你。
EN: I will support you wholeheartedly when you need me.

ZH: 当他来到这个城市时，他立刻喜欢上了这里。
EN: When he came to this city, he immediately fell in love with it.

ZH: 当我生病时，她照顾了我。
EN: When I was sick, she took care of me.

ZH: 当我去饭店时，我点了一份披萨。
EN: When I went to the restaurant, I ordered a pizza.

ZH: 当他看到那只可爱的小狗时，他忍不住笑了。
EN: He couldn’t help but smile when he saw that cute little dog.

ZH: 当我失去了他的时候，我感到无助和寂寞。
EN: When I lost him, I felt helpless and lonely.

