EN: I got very angry when she complained about me.

ZH: 当我们一起唱歌时，我们感到快乐无比。
EN: We feel extremely happy when we sing together.

ZH: 当他们犯了错误时，她总是帮助他们恢复过来。
EN: She always helps them to recover when they make mistakes.

ZH: 当小孩子们看到糖果时，他们的眼睛都发光了。
EN: The children's eyes lit up when they saw the candy.

ZH: 当他下定决心时，没有什么能阻止他。
EN: When he is determined, nothing can stop him.

